   SHOPPING-STRATEGY _ The day after Thanksgiving marks the start
of the busiest shopping season of the year. But while most of us
are just gearing up to fight the crowds, there are those who are
completely finished with their holiday shopping (and, yes, we hate
them). We talk to shoppers who say this is the only way to go if
you want to reduce the stress of the holidays and save money.
(MJohnson, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 21. (WITH PHOTOS).
