<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-11-25 13:31 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9113 &Cx1f; ttj-z
r k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-WONG-COLUMN-HNS &LR;      11-25 0632
