</P>
<P>
   How to calculate the monetary value of a work of Web-based art,
which can be infinitely reproduced? A major acquisition by the
Walker Art Center in Minneapolis highlights the problem but offers
no solution.
</P>
<P>
   SLUGGED: BC-PRICE-TAG-CYBERTIMES-ARTS-NYTSF
