<P>
   PINOCHET (London) _ The House of Lords rejected Gen. Augusto
Pinochet's claim to immunity from arrest, commiting him to remain
in custody here while Spain seeks his extradition on charges of
genocide and terrorism. By Warren Hoge.
</P>
<P>
   With graphic.
</P>
<P>
   TURKEY-POLITICS (Istanbul, Turkey) _ The government of Prime
Minister Mesut Yilmaz, plagued since its inception 17 months ago by
competing pressures from Islamic groups and the rigidly secular
military, lost a confidence vote in Parliament and fell Wednesday.
By Steven Kinzer.
