   With photo and graphic.
</P>
<P>
   UMBILICAL-BLOOD (Undated) _ A comprehensive study finds that
cells derived from the blood in umbilical cords can greatly enhance
recovery from bone marrow transplants and certain kinds of anemia.
The finding is expected to have great impact on treatment. By
Denise Grady.
</P>
