</P>
<P>
   HOLIDAY-SHOPPING (Undated) _ For some time, the nation's
discount department stores have been the big winners in the
shopping wars, with the trend only intensifying this year. They are
expected to reap big gains in the forthcoming Christmas season,
since shoppers are trying to stretch what they spend a little
further. By Sharon R. King.
</P>
