<HEADLINE>
BETTY FRIEDAN SAYS CHILD CARE IS NOW THE KEY ISSUE FOR WOMEN 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (For release Sunday, Nov. 29)   (Filed in ``w'' and ``l'' categories)  
