cadre of loyal students and alum, instilled with Jesuit teachings
of ethics and community service, Brophy College Preparatory has
managed to carve out a lofty niche for itself. With PHOTOS. By BOB
GOLFEN. Story moved in the ``L'' category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
NOTARO-COLUMN (Undated) - It didn't hit me that he was serious
