new!'' ``Those look like running shoes!'' I balked. He took a deep
breath and shot me a look. ``They are running shoes,'' he said,
shaking his head. ``I told you I'm going to run that marathon with
some people at work. We're a team!'' I never believed him. How
could I? We're not even people that walk very fast. By LAURI
NOTARO. Story moved in the ``L'' category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
