   _ How about a scenario to put the Seminoles in the Rose Bowl?
Here's one: UCLA goes to the Fiesta Bowl, Arizona (10-1) loses to
Arizona State, Notre Dame loses to Southern Cal and Kansas State
loses to Texas A&AMP;M. There would be no Pac-10 team to match with
Wisconsin. It's the only big bowl Bobby BowdenWORTH NOTINGDanny
FordTommy WestMax Lennon. The pressure to bring Ford back was
tremendous, but the administrationDeno Curris said no.
