<P>
   CLINTON-SCANDAL (Washington) _ A spokesman for Independent
Counsel Kenneth Starr says at least another 18 months, possibly two
years, will be needed to complete the investigations of President
Clinton that began with the Whitewater land deal and extended to
the president's sexual relationship with a young intern. By JOHN C.
HENRY. (Already filed.)
