   (NYT28) WEST NYACK, N.Y. -- Nov. 25, 1998 -- HOLIDAY-SHOPPING-2,
11-25 -- ``We like the discount stores,'' says John McCormack, with
his grandson in the Target store electronics department at the
Palisades Center mall in West Nyack. ``We definitely buy clothing
in the department stores, but buy most other items in discount
stores.'' (Chris Maynard/New York Times Photo)
</P>
