two sons and baby sitter in the Target store at the Palisades
Center mall in West Nyack. ``To tell you the truth, the value was
great.'' The nation's discount department stores have transformed
themselves into one-stop shopping meccas, expanding product
offerings and adding services. (Chris Maynard/New York Times Photo)
