home fireplace? One possibility is to add inserts that convert the
fireplace into a stove. Wood-burning inserts fit in the fireplace
and use the existing chimney to exhaust smoke and combustion gases.
They have faceplates with metal or glass doors that fit across the
fireplace opening to enclose the fire. (Edward R. Lipinski/New York
