   (ART ADV: Photos [NYT12,13,14) have been sent to NYT photo
clients.)
</P>
<P>
   NY-AUCTIONS (New York) _ An auction on Tuesday, billed by
Christie's on Park Avenue as ``the most valuable and important
collection of European furniture ever to come to auction,'' proves
to be a major disappointment. By William Hamliton.
</P>
